Class OgmImplicitNamingStrategy

  • java.lang.Object

    Serializable, ImplicitNamingStrategy

    public class OgmImplicitNamingStrategy
extends ImplicitNamingStrategyJpaCompliantImpl
    An ImplicitNamingStrategy which exposes component property names via their full path (e.g. "newsId.author") rather than only the actual property name (e.g. "author").
